POMCP 1.0
This is a combination of the POMCP algorithm and ASP reasoning, as presented at AAMAS'23 conference.

# HOW TO RUN

```
build/pomcp --problem rocksample --hardcoded=true --size 12 --number 4 --timeout 100000000 --mindouble 15 --maxdouble 15 --runs 50 --xes 1 --rolloutknowledge=1 --treeknowledge=1 --asp $ASP_NAME;
```

Main parameters are explained with --help

Alternatively, use
```
scripts/run_rocksample.sh
```
to automate run of experiments (adapt to the specific task)

option "xes" allows to save statistics of runs (including time and discounted / undiscounted return)

# NOTE
Refer to rocksample code for a more up to date version

